{
  "texts": [
    "Observe that the call to Vectorize on line 3 in Algorithm 1 only uses inputs from the regulatory authority.",
    "This computation therefore does not have to execute as an MPC circuit.",
    "The regulatory authority can instead provide the -→ D vectors of drones as an input to the algorithm.",
    "(the square of the L2norms), which we simply multiply.",
    "It reveals these values only to the citizen, who can then proceed with the square-root, division and arccos (in plaintext) on their mobile device to compute 𝜙 and shortlist drones accordingly."
  ]
}